:

1. *Los* se njegov život promenio nakon što je otputovao. (His life changed after he travelled.)
2. Ona je bila toliko *losa* u matematici da je morala da popravi ispit. (She was so bad in math that she had to retake the exam.)
3. *Los* odnos između dve zemlje je doveo do rata. (The poor relationship between two countries led to war.)
4. *Losim* vladanjem je doveo svoju zemlju u stanje krize. (His bad governance brought his country into crisis.)
5. *Los* je soj koji je iskoristio da bi postigao svoje ciljeve. (He was a scoundrel who used to achieve his goals.)